      "acceptanceCriteria": "Key model inputs (viscosity, density, hemolysis model constants) are documented with sources.",
      "rationale": "Blood analog fluid properties and hemolysis model constants are sourced from peer-reviewed literature and documented in the simulation report. Sensitivity analysis on input parameters is not required at MRL 2."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Test samples",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Number and selection of test samples documented; traceability to experimental records maintained.",
      "rationale": "Five pump units were tested across the validation campaign; sample selection and traceability are documented. Statistical characterization of inter-unit variability is not required at MRL 2 and is not assessed."
    },
    {
