      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Correspondence between experimental and simulation input parameters is documented; any discrepancies are noted.",
      "rationale": "Input parameter correspondence between in-vitro experiments and CFD simulations is documented in the V&V report appendix. Minor discrepancies in inlet velocity profiles are noted but deemed acceptable at MRL 2 without formal equivalency analysis."
    }
