    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are not assessed, consistent with MRL 2 scope. The CFD model is accepted for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. This model has been applied in clinical research contexts and the overall evidence package supports the device safety claim within the operating envelope evaluated.",
